s/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nApple Watch 好似都已經係Amoled...<br />\n係咪無咩人投訴有印?<br />\n呢個可能真係定律...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/164442_aad4c089680f3ec453f3b7783ad233a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F164442_aad4c089680f3ec453f3b7783ad233a9.jpg&h=232e177f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻錶少用咪冇咁易有印<br />\n我果時部Galaxy S2 半年就有印，仲要講緊當年用電話冇而家咁長時間咁多game 玩，不過就真係慣左個Mon 開到勁光</blockquote><br />\n一係唔用amoled , 實體指紋鎖放後面或側面<br />\n一係用amoled, 有on top screen finger print<br />\n大家會揀邊樣"},{"pid":"82aa54f5030fc2cf5476e2b144967b5c9ec1aa17","tid":314032,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>apple 出就唔會有印，依個係定律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nApple Watch 好似都已經係Amoled...<br />\n係咪無咩人投訴有印?<br />\n呢個可能真係定律...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梗係少人投訴<br />\n你有用AW就知佢個screen on既時間係幾少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你長期着都係有印<br />\n<br />\n利申：用緊"},{"pid":"5f38906ac1f1db07fa3960765b8d73b07cfd5243","tid":314032,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>apple 出就唔會有印，依個係定律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nApple Watch 好似都已經係Amoled...<br />\n係咪無咩人投訴有印?<br />\n呢個可能真係定律...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/164442_aad4c089680f3ec453f3b7783ad233a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F164442_aad4c08